    ğŸ”¹ `gmake -j <number>`    --> ğŸš€ Run the build in multiple processes in parallel, to speed it up.  E.g., `gmake -j4` uses 4 processes.
    ğŸ”¹ `gmake -n`              --> ğŸ§ Show the commands that would be executed, without actually running them.

